 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ucuellar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Cuellar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/26/02 2:31:29 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10440.topic&index=20>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sontelak Strategy</span><hr size=1> AOE fire and AOE fear.<br>
<br>
Line up your MT on one side, everyone else on the other side. Make sure your healers are a litle ways back.  He procs dispell, so if your MT has a fast connectiona nd like 15 instaclick buff items, he should be ablel to keep his buffs, just put ageo/RF/rm in the last few slots.  <br>
<br>
His AOE is hard to resist, but fear isn't.  He pilages everyone directly in front of him, that is why EVERYONE meleeing should be behind him.<br>
<br>
All in all, he's not THAT hard, the problem is that his AOE will rip people to shreds if you don't kill him fast enough. <br>
<br>
You use to have to chain slow him to keep him slowed. I'm pretty sure assonance lands (L60 bard slow), but can't remember, all the dragons sorta blend in together...<br>
<br>
AOE resist songs really help on sont due to the fact that it refreshes if it's dispelled, and also it's stackable.<br>
<br>
Remember to have jboots or another instaclick item in your first slot and when it gets dispelled, reclick it and get it back in the first slot.<br>
<br>
Nothing spectacular in my post, but maybe it will save you 1-2 hours on 1-2 failures figuring the above things out.<br>
<br>
-Cuellar <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/umikitta.showPublicProfile?language=EN>mikitta</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://dmsidelines.hsolutions.net/images/MKcross.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/26/02 2:48:01 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10440.topic&index=21>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> :)</span><hr size=1> For those few of you who have posted useful information, thank you.  Thank you Cuellar for that detailed discussion.  It helps alot, especially since another guild last night wiped 4 times on our server trying Sont (not the first time they had done him btw).<br>
